Constructors

constructor

  • new SimpleDataRecord(data: any, dataSource: DataSource, isOriginData?: boolean): SimpleDataRecord
    • Defined in lib/data-source/ds-base-types.ts:1089

    originData: is the data from the real data source, such as query from remote service/database. data is the data used in Exb.

    The origin data uses this schema: {fieldName: value}, we'll reverse it to {jimuFieldName: value}, which is called data and will be used in exb.

    Parameters

    • data: any
    • dataSource: DataSource
    • Default value isOriginData: boolean = true

    Returns SimpleDataRecord
